1. Install pnpm
   - npm install -g pnpm
2. Create a React project
   - pnpm create react-app project-name --template typescript
3. Delete node_modules, package-lock.json
4 -1. Create a file ".npmrc"
  -2. add  " auto-install-peers=true "
/* -3. remove node_modules               */
/* -4. reinstall packages (pnpm install) */
5. Install Packages using pnpm
   - pnpm install
6. When running dev server : Property 'toBeInTheDocument' does not exist on type 'JestMatchers<HTMLElement>'.
   - pnpm add -D @types/testing-library__jest-dom
7. tsconfig.json
   {
     "exclude": ["node_modules", ".next"]
   }

* package.json ($npm_package_)
// reference to next.js version
